### Track: Live Trading

M3 — Live Execution Service and Broker Credential Wiring
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-12
Notes: LiveExecutionService with mandatory kill switch pre-check, risk gate enforcement, database persistence before broker submission. LiveExecutionServiceInterface, live routes (POST/GET /live/orders, positions, pnl, cancel, sync), KillSwitchActiveError, live:trade scope + live_trader role. 36 new tests (27 service + 9 routes), 2539 total passing, 85.82% coverage.

M4 — Multi-Broker Expansion: Schwab/TD Ameritrade Adapter
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-12
Notes: SchwabConfig Pydantic model (frozen, factory methods, URL properties). SchwabOAuthManager with thread-safe token lifecycle, auto-refresh 120s before expiry, Basic auth to token endpoint. SchwabBrokerAdapter implementing all 12 BrokerAdapterInterface methods: submit/cancel/get/list orders, get fills/positions/account, diagnostics, market hours. OAuth Bearer token injection on every request. Full Schwab status mapping (20 statuses). Error mapping: 401/403→AuthError, 404→NotFoundError, 429/5xx→TransientError. Retry with exponential backoff. 75 new tests (29 auth + 46 adapter), 2651 total passing, 86.40% coverage.

M5 — Live Integration Tests and Performance Validation
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-12
Notes: Full integration test suite validating LiveExecutionService with real SQL repositories (SQLite) + MockBrokerAdapter. test_live_execution_integration.py (14 tests): order lifecycle, kill switch blocking, risk gate enforcement, concurrent submission, deployment validation, idempotency, order sync. test_multi_broker_integration.py (8 tests): parallel broker execution, failover, position/P&L isolation, registry operations. locustfile_live.py: 4 load test scenarios (order throughput, mixed workload, kill switch MTTH, P&L latency). SLO validation report with all 5 SLOs passing. Bug fix: datetime-to-ISO conversion in LiveExecutionService for SQL repo compatibility. 22 new tests, 2727 total passing, 84.41% coverage.

M6 — MinIO Artifact Storage Wiring and Deployment Pipeline
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-12
Notes: TODO ISS-012 resolved. MinIO backend wired into get_artifact_storage() with env-based config (MINIO_ENDPOINT, MINIO_ACCESS_KEY, MINIO_SECRET_KEY, MINIO_SECURE). Lifespan initializes storage on startup with graceful failure handling. DeploymentPipeline service with staging validation gates, promotion with automatic rollback, and audit trail. K8s manifests for staging (1 replica, MinIO HTTP) and production (3 replicas, MinIO TLS, topology spread). Staging-to-production runbook updated with infrastructure promotion procedure. 37 new tests (15 wiring + 22 pipeline), 2576 total passing, 86.32% coverage.

### Track: Trader UX

M7 — Real-Time Position Dashboard (WebSocket)
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-12
Notes: WsMessageType enum and frozen Pydantic message contracts (WsPositionItem, WsPositionUpdate, WsOrderUpdate, WsAccountUpdate, WsFillEvent, WsPnlUpdate, WsMessage envelope). WebSocketConnectionManager with asyncio.Lock, deployment-scoped rooms, dead-connection cleanup on broadcast. ws_positions WebSocket endpoint at /ws/positions/{deployment_id} with JWT auth via query param, connected message, ping/pong. REST /ws/stats for diagnostics. Frontend useWebSocket hook with auto-reconnect, exponential backoff, auth-failure detection (4008 no retry). LiveDashboard component: connection status indicator, account summary cards, positions table with P&L coloring, recent orders with status badges. 50 new tests (14 ws_manager + 6 ws_positions + 13 useWebSocket + 23 LiveDashboard — backend: 2671 passing, 86.51% coverage; frontend: 1227 passing).

M8 — Execution Reports and Order History
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-12
Notes: New contracts: OrderHistoryQuery, OrderHistoryItem, FillItem, OrderHistoryPage, ExecutionReportSummary, SymbolBreakdown, ModeBreakdown (libs/contracts/execution_report.py). Extended ExecutionAnalysisInterface with get_order_history(), get_execution_report(), export_orders_csv(). Service methods: paginated order history with filtering (symbol/side/status/mode/date_range), sorting, CSV export; aggregate metrics with fill_rate, volume, commission, symbol/mode breakdowns. Three new API endpoints: GET /execution-analysis/orders (paginated), GET /execution-analysis/report (aggregates), GET /execution-analysis/export (CSV). Frontend: OrderHistory.tsx (filterable sortable paginated table with status badges, row expansion for fills, CSV export), ExecutionReport.tsx (date-range dashboard with summary cards, symbol/mode breakdowns, latency percentiles). API service layer at features/execution/api.ts. 42 new tests (22 backend + 9 OrderHistory + 11 ExecutionReport). Backend: 2693 passing, 85.67% coverage; frontend: 20 new tests passing, TypeScript clean, ESLint clean.

