Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-12
Notes: Compliance report contracts (ComplianceOrderRecord, ExecutionComplianceReport, BestExecutionRecord, BestExecutionReport, VenueRoutingRecord, VenueRoutingReport, MonthlySummary) in libs/contracts/compliance_report.py. ComplianceReportServiceInterface with 5 abstract methods. ComplianceReportService production implementation with order querying, best execution analysis (slippage vs limit price, fill latency), venue routing aggregation, monthly summaries, CSV export. 5 API endpoints at /compliance/* (execution-report, best-execution, venue-routing, monthly-summary, execution-report/csv), all requiring compliance:read scope. compliance:read added to all RBAC roles. 12 new tests (4 execution report + 2 best execution + 2 venue routing + 2 monthly summary + 2 CSV export). Backend: 2705 passing, 84.31% coverage. Lint clean.

M12 — Audit Trail Export and Retention Policy
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-12
Notes: Full audit export and data retention system. Contracts: AuditExportFormat (JSON/CSV/NDJSON), AuditExportRequest, AuditExportResult (SHA-256 tamper-evident hash), RetentionEntityType (4 types), RetentionPolicyEntry, RetentionPolicyConfig, ArchiveSummary. Interfaces: AuditExportServiceInterface (4 methods), RetentionServiceInterface (3 methods), AuditExportRepositoryInterface (4 methods). Services: AuditExportService (batch fetching, 3 format outputs, gzip compression, SHA-256 hashing), RetentionService (archive expired records past retention period, purge archived records past grace period, entity-type→ORM model mapping). ORM models: ArchivedAuditEvent, ArchivedOrder, AuditExportJob. SQL repository: SqlAuditExportRepository. Routes: POST /audit/export, GET /audit/export/{job_id}, GET /audit/export/{job_id}/content, GET /audit/retention-policy (all scope-protected). Alembic migration 0013 (3 new tables + indexes). 43 new tests (19 export service + 13 retention service + 11 routes). 2052+ backend tests passing. Ruff clean.

M13 — Incident Automation: PagerDuty/Slack Integration
Status: DONE
Completed: 2026-04-12
Notes: Full incident automation system with PagerDuty and Slack integration. Contracts: IncidentSeverity (P1-P4), NotificationChannel (Slack/PagerDuty), AlertTriggerType (7 event types), IncidentStatus (triggered/acknowledged/resolved/escalated), AlertRule, EscalationPolicy, IncidentRecord, NotificationResult. Interfaces: NotificationProviderInterface (send_alert/send_resolution), IncidentRepositoryInterface (save/find_by_id/find_open/find_unacknowledged_past_sla). Providers: SlackNotificationProvider (webhook with severity-coded attachments, connection error handling), PagerDutyNotificationProvider (Events API v2 trigger/resolve, severity mapping P1→critical/P2→error/P3→warning/P4→info, incident_id as dedup_key). IncidentManager: create incident with alert rule matching, dispatch to configured channels, acknowledge/resolve lifecycle, auto-escalation check (P1: 15min, P2: 1hr). NotificationConfig: 7 default alert rules covering all trigger types, 2 escalation policies, factory function with env-based credential wiring. Mock: MockIncidentRepository with SLA query support. 37 new tests (11 providers + 13 incident manager + 13 config). 2089+ backend tests passing. Ruff clean.

